{"id": 115, "genre": 1000, "title": "你期待双十一吗？", "description": "离一年一度的淘宝天猫双十一不到一个月了呢，商家们都开始想点子或者扮傲娇，你有啥想买的吗！\r\n", "record_count": 1298, "comment_count": 27, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194136inaE3GJfds8ScRZr.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2014-10-22T09:26:08Z", "questions": [{"id": 107, "title": "你期待双十一吗？", "content": "你期待双十一吗？", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 918, "content": "我知道会降价的品牌，已经把想要的都放进购物车了", "image": "img/option/option/201606071925213wegkbHDqCJh1SMW.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 919, "content": "我会关心一下可能降价的品牌，看有没有需要的", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192521mQIpaW06i9YwVSqb.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 920, "content": "我会看看商家会出什么新玩法", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192522oktJD7VA0drfzbsO.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 921, "content": "我只操心那个物流啊，慢透了", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192522425JO97lRLdrwqDy.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 922, "content": "我想要的东西都没有参加双十一", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192522WQ1zipu2Fyf7h9ob.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 923, "content": "我总是无法抢到自己想要的东西", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192522VmO6XlKhuFxz3rcS.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 924, "content": "我以前的双十一买了好多没有用的东西", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192522fxbN8Otpzs5wak1G.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 925, "content": "我不觉得双十一真的有很多折扣", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192522hdD7C2YLzgfR41Hu.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 926, "content": "不网购，不关心", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192522y5Yi9zskX7x6ZUgF.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 927, "content": "双十一？我比较关心我还单身这事儿！", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192523UmcOjgSaqo29GJsW.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}